 mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">第二十六条</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"> </font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">国家励志奖学金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">5000</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">/</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">生•年（按国家有关规定评定）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\">   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.02\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">第二十七条</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"> </font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">奖（助）学金（受奖面</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">30%</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）：一等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SI