-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">勤工助学：家庭经济困难的学生可参加学校组织的勤工助学活动，获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">150-240</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">/</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月的报酬，补贴生活、学习费用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\">   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.02\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">第三十一条</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"> </font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">困难补助：学校每年对家庭经济特别困难的学生，进行定期和不定期的现金和实物补助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\">   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.02\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">第三十二条</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"> </font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; F